The paper focuses on emotion analysis of videos using both visual and textual features. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel model for feature extraction and learning, which involves deep learning techniques, making it relevant to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
